莫莉·林沃德 (Molly Ringwald) 表示《早餐俱乐部》还没有“过时” https://www.nme.com/news/film/molly-ringwald-says-the-breakfast-club-hasnt-ged-well-3612898?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=molly-ringwald-says-the-breakfast-俱乐部尚未成熟Elizabeth AubreyWed, 03 Apr 2024 19:03:56 +0000 Film NewsNews https://www.nme.com/?p=3612898 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Molly-Ringwald-Photo-by-Gilbert-Flores_WWD-via-Getty-Images.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="莫莉·林沃德" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Molly-Ringwald-Photo-by-Gilbert-Flores_WWD-via-Getty-Images.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Molly-Ringwald-Photo-by-Gilbert-Flores_WWD-via-Getty-Images-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Molly-Ringwald-Photo-by-Gilbert-Flores_WWD-via-Getty-Images-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Molly-Ringwald-Photo-by-Gilbert-Flores_WWD-via-Getty-Images-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Molly-Ringwald-Photo-by-Gilbert-Flores_WWD-via-Getty-Images-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Molly-Ringwald-Photo-by-Gilbert-Flores_WWD-via-Getty-Images-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> “我很高兴我们能够看到这一点并说现在情况确实有所不同”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/molly-ringwald-says-the-breakfast-club-hasnt-aged-well-3612898">莫莉·林沃德 (Molly Ringwald) 表示《早餐俱乐部》还没有“过时”的</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">《NME》</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Molly-Ringwald-Photo-by-Gilbert-Flores_WWD-via-Getty-Images.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="莫莉·林沃德" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Molly-Ringwald-Photo-by-Gilbert-Flores_WWD-via-Getty-Images.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Molly-Ringwald-Photo-by-Gilbert-Flores_WWD-via-Getty-Images-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Molly-Ringwald-Photo-by-Gilbert-Flores_WWD-via-Getty-Images-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Molly-Ringwald-Photo-by-Gilbert-Flores_WWD-via-Getty-Images-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Molly-Ringwald-Photo-by-Gilbert-Flores_WWD-via-Getty-Images-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Molly-Ringwald-Photo-by-Gilbert-Flores_WWD-via-Getty-Images-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/films/the-breakfast-club"><em>《早餐俱乐部》的</em></a>演员莫莉·林沃德在一次新的采访中表示，这部电影还没有“过时”。</p><p>这部由约翰·休斯导演执导的经典电影将于明年迎来 40 岁生日，在接受<a href="https://www.thetimes.co.uk/article/molly-ringwald-interview-elements-of-the-breakfast-club-havent-aged-well-6mpvv73d8" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener"><em>《泰晤士报》</em></a>采访时，林沃德在接受《泰晤士报》采访时透露了影片中的一些元素。 “还没有老好”。</p><p> “我不喜欢在屏幕上看到自己。我只重看了 1985 年上映的<em>《早餐俱乐部》</em> ，因为（我的女儿）玛蒂尔达想和我一起看，”她在采访中说道。</p><p> “这部电影有很多我非常喜欢的地方，但有些元素还没有过时——比如贾德·尼尔森饰演的约翰·本德，他本质上对我的角色进行了性骚扰。”</p><p>本德和克莱尔在电影接近尾声时亲吻了，但本德反复询问克莱尔的童贞，并在另一时刻抬起她的裙子。</p><p> “我很高兴我们能够看到这一点，并说现在情况确实不同了，”她补充道，在#MeToo 后的背景下谈论这一场景。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="早餐俱乐部官方预告片 #1 - 保罗·格里森电影 (1985) 高清" width="696" height="522" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/BSXBvor47Zs?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>演员艾莉·希迪之前也曾谈到过电影中的元素，称她“从来不喜欢”角色为了变得更有吸引力而进行改造的场景。</p><p> <a href="https://www.independent.co.uk/arts-entertainment/films/features/ally-sheedy-interview-breakfast-club-makeover-john-hughes-molly-ringwald-brat-pack-a9549651.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">2020 年，希迪在接受<em>《独立报》</em></a>采访时表示：“听着，那是八十年代的好莱坞。他们想把丑小鸭变成天鹅。就我而言，这不是我对这个角色所做的，但这就是他们想要的。”</p><p>希迪还<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/molly-ringwald-discomfort-breakfast-club-me-too-movement-2285163-2285163">回应了林沃德在 2018 年撰写的一篇文章，该文章从现代角度审视了这部电影。</a></p><p> “我认为审问这些东西是一件好事，”希迪说。 “这是一件非常好的事情。看看它的哪些部分仍然相关或过时，以及它如何与一些年轻人而不是其他人交谈。”</p><p> 2021 年， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/anthony-michael-hall-reveals-what-john-hughes-had-planned-for-a-breakfast-club-sequel-3078652">安东尼·迈克尔·霍尔 (Anthony Michael Hall) 谈到了导演约翰·休斯 (John Hughes) 拍摄<em>《早餐俱乐部》</em>续集的计划。</a></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/molly-ringwald-says-the-breakfast-club-hasnt-aged-well-3612898">莫莉·林沃德 (Molly Ringwald) 表示《早餐俱乐部》还没有“过时”的</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">《NME》</a>上。</p> ;
 Glass Animals 分享主题曲《Creatures In Heaven》并宣布新专辑《I Love You So F***ing Much》 https://www.nme.com/news/music/glass-animals-share-anthemic-creatures-in-heaven-and-announce-new-album-i-love-you-so-fing-much-3612891？ utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=glass-animals-share-anthemic-creatures-in-heaven-and-announce-new-album-i-love-you-so-fing-muchMax Pilley Wed, 03 Apr 2024 18:42:14 +0000 Music NewsNewsIndiePophttps://www.nme.com/?p=3612891 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/glass_animals_new.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="玻璃动物" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/glass_animals_new.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/glass_animals_new-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/glass_animals_new-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/glass_animals_new-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/glass_animals_new-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/glass_animals_new-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>他们四年来的第一张专辑将于七月发行</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/glass-animals-share-anthemic-creatures-in-heaven-and-announce-new-album-i-love-you-so-fing-much-3612891">Glass Animals 分享了主题曲“Creatures In Heaven”，并宣布新专辑“I Love You So F***ing Much”</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/glass_animals_new.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="玻璃动物" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/glass_animals_new.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/glass_animals_new-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/glass_animals_new-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/glass_animals_new-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/glass_animals_new-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/glass_animals_new-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/glass-animals">Glass Animals</a>带着新单曲《Creatures in Heaven》回归，并宣布推出新专辑《I Love You So F***ing Much》。 </p><ul><li data-leveltext="" data-font="Symbol" data-listid="56" data-list-defn-props="{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559683&quot;:0,&quot;335559684&quot;:-2,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}" aria-setsize="-1" data-aria-posinset="1" data-aria-level="1"><b>阅读更多：</b><b> </b><a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=rhQT_QsaQIw"><b>《Dreamland》中的 Glass Animals、90 年代怀旧情怀以及他们的专辑“扩展包” |谈话中</b></a></li></ul><p>这张专辑将是该乐队职业生涯的第四张完整专辑，也是 2020 年《 <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/glass-animals-dreamland-album-review-2721497">Dreamland</a> 》的后续专辑。它将于 7 月 19 日通过 Polydor 发售，您可以<a href="https://glassanimals.lnk.to/love" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在此处</a>预订。</p><p> 《Creatures in Heaven》是这张专辑的第一个品尝者，在谈到其存在主义主题时，主唱戴夫·贝利 (Dave Bayley) 说道：“这是关于时间上的一个时刻，无论是一瞬间、一年还是其他什么，有能力成为极大地形成和改变生活。就算已经结束了。或者如果事情没有按计划进行。或者如果它死得太早。还是他妈的漂亮啊那一刻的爱、关怀和感觉将永远存在。它永远不会真正死去。如果你选择这样看的话。”</p><p>听下面的曲目： </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="玻璃动物 - 天堂中的生物（可视化工具）" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/RqHbD1i4NF4?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p> <b>“我爱你如此他妈的多”曲目列表：</b> </p><ol><li data-leveltext="%1." data-font="Helvetica" data-listid="57" data-list-defn-props="{&quot;335551671&quot;:1,&quot;335552541&